Package: limbo-backup
Version: 0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, tar, gzip, gnupg, rclone, systemd, coreutils, rsync, openssh-client
Maintainer: Jordi Mock <mockjordi@gmail.com>
Description: Modular backup system with pluggable tasks and modules
 A systemd-timer-driven backup tool that executes configurable backup tasks and applies modular post-processing.
 Supports pre/post commands, file inclusion/exclusion, SFTP uploads, and plugin-style module processing.
